  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prior to the main study we will perform a pilot study on 60 subjects. The purpose of the
      pilot study is to identify the range of odor concentrations that will be used in the main
      study and to optimize the tasks performed in the main study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
